dc_creator_sm: Snohomish County Geographic Information System (GIS), Dept. of Information Services
dc_description_s: This data set shows where urban growth will be encouraged and supported by public facilities and services for the next 20 years. More information is available in the General Policy Plan (GPP).            UrbanGrowth boundaries are spatially registered with parcels from the Integrated Land Records (ILR) data set. Definition of urban growth.             Derivative data is routinely refreshed as the master data set is updated.
dc_publisher_s: Snohomish County (WA) Geographic Information System (Snohomish GIS)
